Privacy Policy
Scope of application
We take privacy and transparency seriously. Thus, we commit to ensure the highest possible protection of your personal data. We collect, process and use your personal data strictly in accordance with the European Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and other applicable legislation.
In the following, we would like to inform you about what information we collect and how we proceed with it. This privacy policy applies both to the use of our Ovy App and to the use of our website. In each case, we will tell you in detail to which specific use (Ovy App, Website, or both) the respective content of this Privacy Policy applies to.
Of course, we are aware that you provide us with highly sensitive personal information especially when using our Ovy App. Your health data is particularly protected since it is a so-called ‘special category of personal data’ according to Article 9 of the GDPR. We process your sensitive data only if you give us your
explicit consent
. Below you will find the content of the consent that we request from you as part of the registration and usage of the Ovy App. Therefore, if you tick the relevant Opt-in box during the registration process, you give us your consent to use your personal information as described in detail below.
To use the Ovy App you must be at least 18 years old.
If you want more information, feel free to contact us at
hello@ovyapp.com
.
